  2. Paste it below as `const firebaseConfig = { ... }`.
  3. In `index.html`, add Firebase SDK scripts (firebase-app and firebase-firestore)
     before `firebase-service.js`, e.g.:

  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.22.1/firebase-app-compat.js"></script>
  <script src="https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/9.22.1/firebase-firestore-compat.js"></script>

  4. Reload the page. The app will use Firestore realtime listeners.

  Example (DO NOT USE THESE KEYS):
*/

